        <item>
            <title>Digital Art Fair 香港西九展告吹，文體旅局：無法評估效益、不批准盛事基金申請</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/02/25/digital-art-fair-cancelled/hottopic/spotlight/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=digital-art-fair-cancelled</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/02/25/digital-art-fair-cancelled/hottopic/spotlight/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 25 Feb 2025 08:00:02 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[城中熱話]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Digital Art Fair]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1293946</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>原定於 3 月 26 日至 30 日在香港西九文化區舉行的 Digital Art Fair（DAF）突然宣佈取消。主辦方指由於「不可控制的原因（Due to reasons beyond our control）」本屆展覽無法如期舉行，並承諾已購票人士可自動獲全額退款，無需辦理任何手續。據本地媒體報道，文化體育及旅遊局（文體旅局）透露，DAF 曾申請文化藝術盛事基金，但未獲批准，當時主辦方已開始發售門票。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1293955" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/2025022532136-694x276.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="276" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/2025022532136-694x276.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/2025022532136.jpg 1239w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><blockquote class="instagram-media" style="background: #FFF; border: 0; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: 0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width: 540px; min-width: 326px; padding: 0; width: calc(100% - 2px);" data-instgrm-captioned="" data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DGcqFHkPmug/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14"><div style="padding: 16px;"><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: row; align-items: center;"><div style="background-color: #f4f4f4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style="background-color: #f4f4f4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style="background-color: #f4f4f4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display: block; height: 50px; margin: 0 auto 12px; width: 50px;"></div><div style="padding-top: 8px;"><div style="color: #3897f0; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 550; line-height: 18px;">在 Instagram 查看這則貼文</div></div><div style="padding: 12.5% 0;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: row; margin-bottom: 14px; align-items: center;"><div><div style="background-color: #f4f4f4; border-radius: 50%; height: 12.5px; width: 12.5px; transform: translateX(0px) translateY(7px);"></div><div style="background-color: #f4f4f4; height: 12.5px; transform: rotate(-45deg) translateX(3px) translateY(1px); width: 12.5px; flex-grow: 0; margin-right: 14px; margin-left: 2px;"></div><div style="background-color: #f4f4f4; border-radius: 50%; height: 12.5px; width: 12.5px; transform: translateX(9px) translateY(-18px);"></div></div><div style="margin-left: 8px;"><div style="background-color: #f4f4f4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 20px; width: 20px;"></div><div style="width: 0; height: 0; border-top: 2px solid transparent; border-left: 6px solid #f4f4f4; border-bottom: 2px solid transparent; transform: translateX(16px) translateY(-4px) rotate(30deg);"></div></div><div style="margin-left: auto;"><div style="width: 0px; border-top: 8px solid #F4F4F4; border-right: 8px solid transparent; transform: translateY(16px);"></div><div style="background-color: #f4f4f4; flex-grow: 0; height: 12px; width: 16px; transform: translateY(-4px);"></div><div style="width: 0; height: 0; border-top: 8px solid #F4F4F4; border-left: 8px solid transparent; transform: translateY(-4px) translateX(8px);"></div></div></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center; margin-bottom: 24px;"><div style="background-color: #f4f4f4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 224px;"></div><div style="background-color: #f4f4f4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 144px;"></div></div><p style="color: #c9c8cd; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 17px; margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 8px; overflow: hidden; padding: 8px 0 7px; text-align: center; text-overflow: ellipsis; white-space: nowrap;"><a style="color: #c9c8cd; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 17px; text-decoration: none;" href="https://www.instagram.com/p/DGcqFHkPmug/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" target="_blank" rel="noopener">DIGITAL ART FAIR（@digitalartfairasia）分享的貼文</a></p></div></blockquote><p><script async src="//www.instagram.com/embed.js"></script></p><p>DAF 由 2020 年創辦，今年原為第五屆展覽。活動曾列入香港旅遊發展局推介項目，惟現時相關網頁已被移除。上星期主辦單位仍宣佈展覽將設有六大主題展區，並引入户外大型 3D 投影技術，計劃把西九文化區大草坪設定成沉浸式藝術空間，務求為觀眾帶來耳目一新的體驗。策展團隊曾邀請多位國際藝術家參與，包括 Krista Kim、中國新媒體藝術家程然，以及土耳其數碼藝術先鋒 Refik Anadol。展覽目標是透過「科技 X 藝術」的概念，帶來融合國際視野和本地特色的創新藝術體驗。截至目前，主辦方未有交代取消展覽的具體原因。購票人士將自動獲退款，毋須額外申請。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1293954" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/2025022532127-694x267.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="267" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/2025022532127-694x267.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/2025022532127.jpg 1256w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>文體旅局早前回應本地傳媒查詢時表示，DAF 曾申請文化藝術盛事基金，惟未有詳細闡述活動內容，亦未提交足夠資料，以致局方無法評估其文藝水平、經濟效益及旅遊吸引力，最終未能批准該資助申請。文體旅局補充，DAF 在申請基金時已開始發售門票。局方藉此提醒，任何主辦機構應及早規劃資金運用，以免因資源不足而臨時取消活動，導致退票等後續問題。</p><p>資料來源：<a href="https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%A5%BF%E4%B9%9D-digital-art-fair-%E5%8F%96%E6%B6%88-%E6%8C%87%E5%8E%9F%E5%9B%A0%E3%80%8C%E7%84%A1%E6%B3%95%E6%8E%A7%E5%88%B6%E3%80%8D-%E6%9B%BE%E5%88%97%E5%85%A5%E6%97%85%E7%99%BC%E5%B1%80%E6%8E%A8%E4%BB%8B%E6%B4%BB%E5%8B%95%EF%B8%B1yahoo-090525190.html">Yahoo</a>、<a href="https://www.orangenews.hk/hongkong/1257430/%E6%95%B8%E5%AD%97%E8%97%9D%E8%A1%93%E5%8D%9A%E8%A6%BD%E6%9C%83%E5%AE%A3%E5%B8%83%E5%8F%96%E6%B6%88-%E6%96%87%E9%AB%94%E6%97%85%E5%B1%80-%E7%94%B3%E8%AB%8B%E7%9B%9B%E4%BA%8B%E5%9F%BA%E9%87%91%E4%B8%8D%E6%9E%9C.shtml">橙新聞</a></p><p>======</p><p>加入 <a href="https://www.threads.net/@unwirehk" target="_blank" rel="noopener">unwire thread</a> 傾傾科技背後黑暗事</p><p>========</p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2025/02/25/digital-art-fair-cancelled/hottopic/spotlight/">Digital Art Fair 香港西九展告吹，文體旅局：無法評估效益、不批准盛事基金申請</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
